      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Need Help Optimizing Your Shopify Store?</h3>
      <p class="mb-4">I specialize in Shopify performance optimization and can help you implement these strategies to improve your store's speed and conversion rates.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-primary text-white rounded-md hover:bg-secondary transition-colors">Get a Performance Audit</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BlogLayout>